The nation's newest aircraft carrier, the Gerald R. Ford, will be commissioned at Norfolk Naval Station on Saturday, July 22, 2017. The ship was photographed at the pier on Wednesday, July 19, 2017. 


Steve Earley | The Virginian-Pilot

























