Gerald J. Ford - Wikipedia




















 






Gerald J. Ford

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Gerald J. Ford[1]


Born
Pampa, TX


Residence
Dallas, Texas, United States[1]


Nationality
American


Education
Doctor of Jurisprudence, Bachelor of Arts / Science[1]


Alma mater
Southern Methodist University[1]


Occupation
Chairman & CEO


Net worth
US$ 2.1 billion (September 2015)[1]


Gerald J. Ford (born 1944) is an American businessman.[1][2][3]



